Description: This file is a custom restore file with no custom logos, hactivation, and the default partition sizes. This file can be used to restore your jailbroken iPhone 3G (old bootrom) to version 4.0.

What is hactivation? Hacktivation is used for non-official carriers such as T-Mobile, instead of activating your iPhone with iTunes it is automatically activated.

